# AI Development Context Rules

# Mandatory reference for any AI-assisted development
# Read docs/ai_guidelines/ before modifying core logic

RULE_ARCH_BLUEPRINT: docs/ai_guidelines/architecture.md
RULE_DATA_CONTRACT: docs/ai_guidelines/schema.md
RULE_WORKFLOW_SOP: docs/ai_guidelines/workflow.md

# Global Constraints
- Backend logic must reside in services/, never in routers.
- US Market quotes must use Sina Direct via AkShareProvider.
- All financial floats must be sanitized via sanitize_float().
- No placeholder code. All features must be fully implemented and documented.
